Package bioLockJ.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BashScriptUtil
    This class generates the bash scripts based on the lines provided by the metagenomeClassifier.
    ConfigUtil
    ConfigUtil reads in the properties file and is used to initialize the root directory.
    MailUtil
    A simple Mail utility to send notifications when job is complete with a status message and summary details about failures and run time.
    MetadataUtil
    The metadataUtil helps access and modify data in the metadata & descriptor files.
    ProcessUtil
    ProcessUtil enables the Java program to execute scripts on thos host OS.
